    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for MRL 2. The CFD model is assessed as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Regulatory submission to FDA 510(k) pathway is supported.",
